{"tid":712734,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"獅山剪影　港攝影師揚威國際","createTime":"2018-06-22T10:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T23:36:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"54ec38161b6b7feccc2f6fcb769e5393e7868f27","tid":712734,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:28:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180622/20428011\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180622%2F20428011&d=PuaKngDH%2FZM%2BerZQRb5l9dibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=7e35048c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180622%2F20428011&h=582a1daf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180622/20428011</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月22日 <br />\n<br />\n獅山剪影　港攝影師揚威國際<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180622/large/22la8p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180622%2Flarge%2F22la8p1.jpg&h=e1f0fc20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n謝國劬作品<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港攝影師謝國劬憑一幅獅子山下萬家燈火的作品，成功在全球57,489幅參賽作品中脫穎而出，勇奪2018年全球大自然攝影比賽「城市與大自然」組別大獎。家住黃大仙的他說，自己名副其實在獅子山下成長，香港人口及城市密度高，親近大自然幫助減低工作及生活上的壓力，並寄語香港必須保留足夠的自然環境。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n評審：呈現人與大自然關係<br />\n<br />\n謝國劬的作品在今年1月14日晚上7時在大帽山山頂拍攝，呈現夜幕低垂時，獅子山峯在山下一幢又一幢高樓的萬家燈火下剪影，相片上方是九龍東一帶，下方是沙田。他表示，獅子山是香港標誌性山麓，亦代表港人努力奮鬥的精神。每逢假期，他都喜歡上山下海，只要全心投入保護好大自然，大自然就會展示獨特美麗一面，也就是一幅幅美麗照片。<br />\n<br />\n今次攝影比賽由大自然保護協會舉辦，收到57,489幅來自135個國家及地區的作品，當中3,502幅來自香港。協會亞太區總幹事Charles Bedford指，謝國劬作品呈現了在香港這個繁華都市中，人類與大自然密不可分關係，期望今次攝影比賽啟發更多人探索及欣賞自身與大自然間的微妙關係。<br />\n<br />\n■記者潘柏林  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n97歲母病重68歲女相認　一刻相擁等了45年<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n蕭定一爆張智霖拆賬佔88%"},{"pid":"225b3c66dd301ed58332d998067fc593f9328906","tid":712734,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65f2d159cd813eff3dab2922410f24a19128a6e","tid":712734,"uid":19725,"like":2,"dislike":26,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:18:54.000Z","msg":"無kelvin 個張咁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb67f7c8e136eb7f825a0f64a5f3654758b8d5f","tid":712734,"uid":11779,"like":7,"dislike":15,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T01:07:33.000Z","msg":"屎味屎影得仲靚過佢。呢啲比賽太多人參加 啲評審跟住求9其揀張就算，點會真係睇<br />\n申利：做過評審。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a669efc4a086acb21326c5e4f17d0249b5f8224","tid":712734,"uid":14625,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"eeb67f7c8e136eb7f825a0f64a5f3654758b8d5f","tid":712734,"uid":11779,"like":7,"dislike":15,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T01:07:33.000Z","msg":"屎味屎影得仲靚過佢。呢啲比賽太多人參加 啲評審跟住求9其揀張就算，點會真係睇<br />\n申利：做過評審。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T02:43:59.000Z","msg":"一睇就知你唔知評審點work<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e845077a79be7179bce7264bc7a5803f57d46c1f","tid":712734,"uid":54436,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T02:47:48.000Z","msg":"航拍影？"},{"pid":"3ae0f2f11a775a46767e3747ebb7190116f6c926","tid":712734,"uid":14476,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T02:56:21.000Z","msg":"咁樣嘅畫質同雜訊都可以拎到獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ccb853eaf1319443ef073c1458cb9836377af29","tid":712734,"uid":14625,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"3ae0f2f11a775a46767e3747ebb7190116f6c926","tid":712734,"uid":14476,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T02:56:21.000Z","msg":